#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/connect.rst:115
msgid ""
"Once the IoT system is connected to the Odoo database, it is displayed as a "
"card in the IoT app. Click the card to access the IoT system's form, which "
"allows to access the :ref:`IoT box's <iot/iot-box/homepage>` "
"or :ref:`Windows virtual IoT's <iot/windows-iot/homepage>` homepage and view "
"the list of :doc:`devices <devices>` connected to the IoT system."
msgstr ""
"Una vez que el sistema IoT esté conectado a la base de datos de Odoo, se "
"muestra como una tarjeta en la aplicación IoT. Haz clic en la tarjeta para "
"acceder al formulario del sistema IoT, que permite acceder a la página de "
"inicio del :ref:`IoT box <iot/iot-box/homepage>` o del :ref:`IoT virtual de "
"Windows <iot/windows-iot/homepage>` y ver la lista de :doc:`dispositivos "
"<devices>` conectados al sistema IoT."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/connect.rst:121
msgid ""
"Enable the :ref:`developer mode <developer-mode>` to access the IoT "
"system's :guilabel:`Technical Information`, such as its :guilabel:`Domain "
"Address`, :guilabel:`Image Version`, and :ref:`SSL Certificate <iot/connect/"
"https_certificate>` :guilabel:`End Date`. By default, drivers are "
"automatically :ref:`updated <iot_updating_iot/handlers>` every time the IoT "
"system is restarted. To disable automatic updates, uncheck "
"the :guilabel:`Automatic drivers update` option."
msgstr ""
"Activa el :ref:`modo de desarrollador <developer-mode>` para acceder a "
"la :guilabel:`Información técnica` del sistema IoT, como "
"su :guilabel:`Dirección de dominio`, :guilabel:`Versión de imagen` "
"y :ref:`Certificado SSL <iot/connect/https_certificate>` :guilabel:`Fecha de "
"finalización`. Por defecto, los controladores se :ref:`actualizan "
"<iot_updating_iot/handlers>` automáticamente cada vez que se reinicia el "
"sistema IoT. Para desactivar las actualizaciones automáticas, desmarca la "
"opción :guilabel:`Actualización automática de controladores`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/connect.rst:127
msgid ""
"On the :ref:`IoT system's form <iot/connect/IoT-form>`, click "
"the :guilabel:`Test` button to test the connection between the IoT system "
"and Odoo and assess the quality of the system's Internet connection."
msgstr ""
"En el :ref:`formulario del sistema IoT <iot/connect/IoT-form>`, haz clic en "
"el botón :guilabel:`Probar` para probar la conexión entre el sistema IoT y "
"Odoo y evaluar la calidad de la conexión a Internet del sistema."

