msgstr ""
"Haz clic en :guilabel:`Continuar` y establece el valor de :guilabel:`Model` "
"en :guilabel:`DYMO LabelWriter 450 DUO Label (en)` (o en el modelo de "
"impresora DYMO que se esté usando)."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/devices/printer.rst:394
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Modify Printer` to set the new driver; a confirmation page "
