"sistema, es decir, tiene un controlador de tipo :guilabel:`RAW` , "
"entonces :ref:`actualiza los controladores del dispositivo <printer/dymo/"
"update_drivers>`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/devices/printer.rst:412
msgid ""
"To resolve the delay issue after modifying the driver, reinstall the printer:"
msgstr ""
