msgstr ""
"En la siguiente página, en la sección :guilabel:`Impresoras locales` , "
"selecciona la impresora preinstalada :guilabel:`DYMO LabelWriter 450 DUO "
"Label (DYMO LabelWriter 450 DUO Label)` (o el modelo de impresora DYMO que "
"se esté usando). Haz clic en :guilabel:`Continuar`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/devices/printer.rst:0
msgid ""
"Add a printer screen on OpenPrinting CUPS with DYMO LabelWriter 450 DUO "
"Label\n"
"highlighted."
msgstr ""
"Pantalla de añadir impresora en OpenPrinting CUPS con DYMO LabelWriter 450 "
"DUO Label\n"
"resaltada."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/devices/printer.rst:425
msgid ""
"On the following screen, update the :guilabel:`Name` to something easily "
