#~ "necesidad:"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "Use Country: This is the easiest way when your data come from CSV files "
#~ "that have been created manually."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Usar País: Ésta es lo forma más sencilla cuando los datos provienen de "
#~ "archivos CSV que se han creado manualmente."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "Use Country/Database ID: You should rarely use this notation. It's mostly "
#~ "used by developers as it's main advantage is to never have conflicts (you "
#~ "may have several records with the same name, but they always have a "
#~ "unique Database ID)"
#~ msgstr ""
